了一首歌曲“反对冰岛的养鱼业”。</p><p>她在一份声明中说：“冰岛拥有欧洲最大的未受破坏的自然环境，至今夏天仍有羊群在山中自由漫步。” “它的鱼在我们的湖泊、河流和峡湾中自由游动。因此，当冰岛和挪威商人开始在我们大部分峡湾购买养鱼场时，这是一个巨大的冲击，并成为今年夏天的主要话题。我们不明白他们是如何能够在十年来几乎没有任何法规阻止的情况下做到这一点。</p><p> “This has already had devastating effect on wildlife and the farmed fish are suffering in horrid health conditions and since a lot of them have escaped, they have started changing the DNA in the Icelandic salmon to the worse and could eventually lead to its extinction.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bjork-fan-goes-viral-with-disturbing-halloween-spin-on-iconic-swan-dress-3525927">Björk fan goes viral with disturbing Halloween spin on iconic swan dress</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
